            <p class="text-gray-400">
              Experience working in agile teams, mentoring junior developers, and contributing to a positive team culture.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-750 transition-colors">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-purple-300">Adaptability</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">
              Quick to learn new technologies and adapt to changing requirements in fast-paced development environments.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
